
---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
  </head>
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <h1>About Me</h1>

      <p>My name is Curtney King. I am a New York City asphalt worker, creator, builder, and lifelong learner.</p>

      <p>I believe growth comes from discipline, curiosity, and a willingness to build things that others never attempt.</p>

      <p>Through Journey to Greatness, I document ideas, projects, books, and experiments that explore history, technology, science, finance, and personal development.</p>

      <p>Some of my work includes:</p>

      <ul>
        <li>There's Two Boats: The Lost Choices of Black History</li>
        <li>Universal Mechanics</li>
        <li>NYC Pavement Digital Twin</li>
        <li>AI Comic-to-Movie System</li>
      </ul>

      <p>My mission is simple:</p>

      <p><strong>"We Don't Work The Same."</strong></p>

      <p>This website serves as a record of the journey, the lessons learned, and the ideas still being built.</p>
    </main>
    <Footer />
  </body>
</html>
